12.short_description: We connect businesses and consumers in LATAM using a peer to peer network of digital marketing agents and a local recommendations community

18.description:
Gran Titán

A unique Local Citizen’s Peer to Peer Recommendations Community and Marketing Platform designed to engage millions of our consumers members to find and share useful information as well as to discover and connect with the most trusted local businesses, brands and independent experts across every corner of Latin America. 

Our Business Vision for Latin America’s 700 million population includes 3 strategic sides: 

Vision #1) A Gran Titán Authorized Digital Marketing Agent and Trusted Titan in every Neighborhood across LATAM.

Vision #2) A Gran Titán Local Citizen's Community Member in every Family across LATAM. 

Vision #3) A Gran Titan Business and Digital Marketing Circle Member in every Block across LATAM. 

OUR DETAILED BUSINESS VISION:

Vision #1) A Gran Titán Authorized Digital Marketing Agent and Trusted Titan in every Neighborhood across Latin America.

“Gran Titan’s Authorized Agents Program of Digital Marketing Trusted Titans"

Designed for independent agents interested in earning monthly income, working remotely as well as on their own schedule; and at the same time obtain free training, certifications, and distinctions for their skills, experience, and achievements in their Digital Marketing activities within the program. 

The Gran Titán Digital Marketing Titans Program provides our authorized Titan agents real practical experience in Digital Marketing through an easy, profitable, and fun system, which our Titans follow step by step using the exclusive and private mobile application on their Digital Marketing activities. 

Those who are accepted and become Authorized Titans enter the program without any initial investment and earn monthly income by distributing and publishing their own personally branded portfolio of free publications featuring locally selected content, brands, businesses and experts highlighted as "Trusted Recommendations" among their family, friends, and on their social networks. 

Additionally, to distributing their own free publications containing hundreds of useful contents and selected offers, Titans selectively and periodically send targeted individual offers as trusted recommendations based on the demographic attributes of their contacts using the exclusive Titans Marketing app. This process generates highly qualified leads for online and offline closing of deals to our premium vendors on offers such as loans and insurance, among many other categories.

These offers as received by each Titan's private network of contacts, are then converted online or assigned automatically to professional sales teams in charge of assisting, quoting and closing sales with the Titan’s generated prospects, earning commissions for the Titan whose publication or initial offer generated each lead. 

Titans gradually develop expertise as recommenders on specific product and service categories, empowering them to be recognized as actual nano and micro influencers within their own network and community within certain categories and eventually being appointed and acting as certain local businesses or brand’s ambassadors and influencers within the community and general market.  This provides them with additional benefits and income as well as great confidence, motivation, experience and clarity about their future professional goals and purposes. 

Titans can also generate income helping their business owners, managers and independent experts within their contacts by helping them to use the Gran Titán marketing platform to promote their own business, brand, or service within the local community, using free directories, ads, content, and reviews, as well as paid campaign services. 

During their time in the program, our authorized Titans develop a strong digital identity and reputation, as well as practical skills and superior competitive advantages to effectively accelerate their entry and fast progress in the job market using their Gran Titán Certificated distinctions and experience, or to successfully continue their career as independent digital entrepreneurs. 

Vision #2) A Gran Titán Local Citizen's Community Member in every Family across LATAM

“Gran Titán’s Local Citizen's Community of Trusted Recommendations”

For most modern and busy adults, it is challenging and time-consuming to obtain local and reliable recommendations for businesses, brands, places, deals, and known experts that help them save time, money, and effectively address the areas that matter most in their lives. 

Free membership in the local citizen community of Gran Titán is the simplest and quickest way to receive, find, share and request trustworthy local recommendations. Members easily discover, interact, and connect with the most trusted local brands, businesses, and experts using reviews, content, directories and trust votes rankings among the network of local community members. 

Additional to their free online community access, members are eligible to free subscriptions of monthly digital magazines which include selected inspiring, uplifting and empowering contents on the things that matter most to each member such as money, health, and pets among 25 different subject matter digital publications. 

Those Recommendations highlighted as "Gran Titán Trusted Selections", are also eligible for an optional money-back guarantee coverage providing our members with peace of mind while making purchasing decisions with selected brands, businesses or experts. 

Additionally, the community offers monthly fun contests, benefits and prizes to members who experience not only savings, and valuable information but also an engaging a rewarding experience. 

Optionally and at no cost, members can also choose an authorized Digital Marketing Titan and designate them as their "Digital Marketing Trusted Titan", who automatically becomes a permanently accessible point of contact to assist their assigned members in finding reliable recommendations and contacts within the community network. 

This "Trusted Titan" is also capable and certified to help their assigned members whenever they need to use the Gran Titán marketing platform to promote their own business, brand, or service within the local community, using free directories, ads, content, and reviews, as well as premium selected services. 

Membership in the community allows citizens to save time and money by providing easy, permanent, and online access to reliable local recommendations, updated content, trends, offers, and exclusive benefits. It offers a permanent, updated, and unique and engaging source of locally shared help, advice, and knowledge, contributing to making better decisions and achieving continuous progress in the areas that matter most in life. 

Vision #3) A Gran Titan Business and Digital Marketing Circle Member in every Block across Latin America.

“Gran Titán’s Local Business and Digital Marketing Circle”

A free membership Local Business Network and Digital Marketing Platform designed specifically for Small and Medium local brands, businesses and independent experts across every corner of Latin America.  

Gran Titán’s Business Circle free membership provides affiliated local businesses, brands  and independent experts with easy, permanent and effective ways to be digitally discovered, locally recommended and instantly connected with millions of ideal customers using Gran Titan’s Digital Marketing Platform’s multiple free advertising and marketing resources, as well as many other benefits that constantly help them grow their local brands and businesses in Latin America. 

Local Businesses, brands and independent experts Members have easy access to: 

Free Help and advice from an assigned trusted and authorized marketing Agent of your choice 

Free access to a network of promotional Marketing Listings Points of Contact: community, directories, lists, rankers, publications as well as paid highlights and premium marketing platform services. 

Each Merchant can build his or her own Recommendations and Influencers Network.

Free marketing mobile applications for SMBs.
  
Online reviews and reputation management

Management of merchants social medida content from a console.
